Re: Bathroom humor
by Hyperworm » Fri 07.03.2009 8:46 am I think your translation is right but your interpretation is wrong.I think the 詰まりの原因 is politely omitted, and could be represented in a translation by "it"."Please flush after use, because [otherwise] it causes (the toilet) to get clogged"Perhaps, above a urinal is the wrong place for this sign...??
